WEBVTT

00:01:24.519 --> 00:01:25.319
Hello?

00:01:27.079 --> 00:01:27.920
Mr. Jiao.

00:01:28.719 --> 00:01:29.519
Mr. Jiao.

00:01:29.680 --> 00:01:30.480
Jiao Shiheng.

00:01:30.519 --> 00:01:32.519
Looks like this guy's time is up.

00:01:32.760 --> 00:01:33.439
Tomorrow night?

00:01:33.439 --> 00:01:34.959
Tomorrow night might not work.

00:01:35.400 --> 00:01:36.719
I have plans tomorrow night.

00:01:37.280 --> 00:01:38.120
What?

00:01:38.599 --> 00:01:39.280
Tomorrow night?

00:01:39.280 --> 00:01:40.879
I've affected the main plot!

00:01:40.959 --> 00:01:41.760
Damn it.

00:01:47.159 --> 00:01:47.959
Hello?

00:01:48.280 --> 00:01:49.120
Mr. Jiao.

00:01:49.120 --> 00:01:50.519
Mengyun will definitely be there tomorrow night.

00:01:50.719 --> 00:01:52.000
Why does this voice sound so familiar?

00:01:52.319 --> 00:01:53.120
Lu Chengwen.

00:01:53.120 --> 00:01:54.319
You're up to your tricks again.

00:01:54.680 --> 00:01:55.480
Chengwen.

00:01:55.920 --> 00:01:56.920
Are you...

00:01:56.920 --> 00:01:58.799
asking me to go on a date with Jiao Shiheng?

00:02:00.159 --> 00:02:00.959
Well...

00:02:01.159 --> 00:02:03.319
we can watch a movie any day.

00:02:03.319 --> 00:02:04.680
He probably has something to discuss with you.

00:02:04.680 --> 00:02:05.879
Why don't you see him first?

00:02:08.479 --> 00:02:09.520
If you don't go,

00:02:09.680 --> 00:02:11.120
I won't be able to explain it.

00:02:11.360 --> 00:02:12.159
Chengwen.

00:02:12.479 --> 00:02:13.120
Since

00:02:13.120 --> 00:02:14.560
you want me to go on a date with him,

00:02:14.919 --> 00:02:16.520
then I'll do as you wish.

00:02:19.360 --> 00:02:19.879
Hello?

00:02:19.879 --> 00:02:20.680
Mr. Jiao.

00:02:21.319 --> 00:02:23.080
Didn't you want to treat me to dinner tomorrow?

00:02:23.080 --> 00:02:24.080
I accept.

00:02:24.479 --> 00:02:25.479
However,

00:02:25.479 --> 00:02:27.080
the time needs to be changed to tonight.

00:02:27.800 --> 00:02:28.599
Really?

00:02:29.080 --> 00:02:29.479
Great, great, great.

00:02:29.479 --> 00:02:30.360
I'll arrange it right away.

00:02:32.599 --> 00:02:33.400
Tonight?

00:02:33.479 --> 00:02:34.599
This is tomorrow's plot!

00:02:34.599 --> 00:02:35.400
Stop messing around!

00:02:35.520 --> 00:02:36.919
Gu Zhantian won't be able to save you this way.

00:02:36.919 --> 00:02:38.400
You'll really be ruined by that beast Jiao Shiheng!

00:02:41.280 --> 00:02:42.080
Mengyun.

00:02:42.319 --> 00:02:43.080
Um...

00:02:43.120 --> 00:02:44.080
Today, you

00:02:44.080 --> 00:02:45.159
can't have dinner with him.

00:02:45.159 --> 00:02:45.960
You can do it tomorrow.

00:02:45.960 --> 00:02:46.800
Because tomorrow...

00:02:47.479 --> 00:02:48.280
Anyway,

00:02:48.479 --> 00:02:50.199
he's just not a good person.

00:02:50.400 --> 00:02:51.199
Chengwen.

00:02:51.879 --> 00:02:53.080
You asked me to go on a date with him,

00:02:53.080 --> 00:02:53.960
and I agreed.

00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:55.520
Now you're saying he's not a good person.

00:02:55.520 --> 00:02:56.919
I don't understand what you mean.

00:02:57.479 --> 00:02:58.919
Anyway, you can't go today.

00:02:58.919 --> 00:03:00.120
Jiao Shiheng will drug you.

00:03:00.120 --> 00:03:00.919
You know?

00:03:01.159 --> 00:03:01.960
Drug me?

00:03:02.960 --> 00:03:04.719
How do you know he'll drug me?

00:03:04.919 --> 00:03:05.680
I...

00:03:05.680 --> 00:03:06.879
You two conspired together,

00:03:06.879 --> 00:03:07.479
right?

00:03:07.479 --> 00:03:08.000
So,

00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:09.319
you asked me to go on a date with him.

00:03:09.479 --> 00:03:10.319
No.

00:03:10.680 --> 00:03:11.479
Well...

00:03:12.120 --> 00:03:13.599
How could I?

00:03:14.080 --> 00:03:15.479
He just screwed over Leng Qingqiu today,

00:03:15.479 --> 00:03:16.400
and I beat him up.

00:03:16.400 --> 00:03:17.599
How could I conspire with him?

00:03:17.599 --> 00:03:18.400
Enough!

00:03:18.400 --> 00:03:20.080
You hit him for Leng Qingqiu,

00:03:20.319 --> 00:03:21.280
and now

00:03:21.280 --> 00:03:22.560
you're giving me to him as compensation,

00:03:22.560 --> 00:03:23.360
right?

00:03:23.479 --> 00:03:25.159
To think that after seeing your performance at the press conference yesterday,

00:03:25.159 --> 00:03:26.319
I actually thought you had changed.

00:03:26.800 --> 00:03:27.800
I didn't expect

00:03:27.800 --> 00:03:29.599
you're still a scumbag who treats women as playthings.

00:03:31.520 --> 00:03:32.280
Chen Mengyun.

00:03:32.560 --> 00:03:34.120
You can't go to dinner with him today.

00:03:34.199 --> 00:03:35.280
Who are you to me?

00:03:35.400 --> 00:03:36.599
What right do you have to control me?

00:03:36.800 --> 00:03:37.840
Right now,

00:03:37.840 --> 00:03:39.319
I'm going on a date with Jiao Shiheng.

00:03:39.400 --> 00:03:40.360
We'll get a room tonight,

00:03:40.360 --> 00:03:41.479
and get engaged next week.

00:03:41.599 --> 00:03:43.400
Our wedding will even be before yours and Leng Qingqiu's!

00:03:45.919 --> 00:03:46.719
No.

00:03:48.719 --> 00:03:51.080
Now Xu Xuejiao, Leng Qingqiu, and Jiang Shihan,

00:03:51.080 --> 00:03:52.919
the key events of the three female leads,

00:03:52.919 --> 00:03:53.759
have all been altered because of me,

00:03:53.879 --> 00:03:55.400
leaving Gu Zhantian with no way to intervene.

00:03:55.800 --> 00:03:57.479
If Chen Mengyun's side also...

00:04:03.520 --> 00:04:05.159
I can't keep ruining the plot.

00:04:10.560 --> 00:04:11.360
What?

00:04:11.879 --> 00:04:12.680
Keep looking.

00:04:14.680 --> 00:04:15.479
Young Master.

00:04:15.719 --> 00:04:16.480
Our brothers...

00:04:16.480 --> 00:04:17.920
Still haven't found Gu Zhantian.

00:04:18.800 --> 00:04:20.480
I have to swallow my pride again.

00:04:42.360 --> 00:04:43.319
Piece of shit.

00:04:43.720 --> 00:04:45.079
Just to make you worry.

00:04:58.800 --> 00:04:59.279
Hello?

00:04:59.279 --> 00:05:00.079
What's wrong?

00:05:00.120 --> 00:05:00.920
Qingqiu.

00:05:01.120 --> 00:05:01.920
Well...

00:05:01.920 --> 00:05:03.720
I need to find Gu Zhantian right now.

00:05:03.720 --> 00:05:05.480
I just had a fight with Chen Mengyun.

00:05:05.519 --> 00:05:06.480
She got mad and went out to find...

00:05:06.480 --> 00:05:07.759
that Jiao Shiheng for dinner.

00:05:08.399 --> 00:05:10.079
Now I must find Gu Zhantian immediately.

00:05:10.079 --> 00:05:11.360
Only Gu Zhantian can find her.

00:05:11.759 --> 00:05:12.920
You piece of shit.

00:05:12.920 --> 00:05:13.920
Stop bothering me.

00:05:20.680 --> 00:05:21.480
Lu Chengwen.

00:05:21.920 --> 00:05:23.199
Whatever is going on between you and Chen Mengyun,

00:05:23.199 --> 00:05:24.319
I'm really not interested.

00:05:24.680 --> 00:05:25.600
Can you stop bothering me?

00:05:25.600 --> 00:05:26.959
Nothing happened between us.

00:05:27.279 --> 00:05:29.279
The most important thing now is to find Gu Zhantian.

00:05:29.279 --> 00:05:31.519
Chen Mengyun went out to eat with Jiao Shiheng.

00:05:31.519 --> 00:05:32.959
Jiao Shiheng will very likely drug her.

00:05:32.959 --> 00:05:34.279
Only Gu Zhantian can save her.

00:05:34.279 --> 00:05:35.360
I can't just watch her get hurt.

00:05:35.360 --> 00:05:36.160
I don't care.

00:05:36.959 --> 00:05:37.759
Drug her?

00:05:38.120 --> 00:05:39.319
I can't find Gu Zhantian.

00:05:39.600 --> 00:05:40.480
But...

00:05:40.480 --> 00:05:42.120
I can check Jiao Shiheng's itinerary for you.

00:05:42.279 --> 00:05:43.680
I'll send you the location right away.

00:05:46.759 --> 00:05:47.560
Gangzi.

00:05:48.279 --> 00:05:49.680
Go to Haicheng Holiday Hotel.

00:05:49.680 --> 00:05:50.879
Call all the brothers.

00:05:51.199 --> 00:05:52.000
Copy that.

00:06:09.600 --> 00:06:10.480
Let me go!

00:06:11.879 --> 00:06:12.680
Let me go!

00:06:17.920 --> 00:06:18.759
Let me go!

00:06:18.879 --> 00:06:19.120
Mengyun.

00:06:19.120 --> 00:06:20.000
You're so beautiful.

00:06:20.000 --> 00:06:20.800
Help!

00:06:26.279 --> 00:06:27.079
Help!

00:06:29.680 --> 00:06:30.519
What are you doing?

00:06:33.199 --> 00:06:33.720
Lu Chengwen!

00:06:33.720 --> 00:06:34.519
Are you crazy?

00:06:34.680 --> 00:06:35.480
Drag him out!

00:06:35.720 --> 00:06:36.720
This time, beat him hard.

00:06:36.720 --> 00:06:37.480
Beat him to death!

00:06:37.480 --> 00:06:37.759
Yes, sir!

00:06:38.920 --> 00:06:39.439
Chengwen.

00:06:39.879 --> 00:06:40.680
Save me, Chengwen.

00:06:40.680 --> 00:06:41.279
Are you okay?

00:06:41.279 --> 00:06:42.000
I told you not to come.

00:06:42.000 --> 00:06:42.800
But you insisted.

00:06:43.120 --> 00:06:43.920
Chengwen.

00:06:44.079 --> 00:06:44.519
Why are you so hot?

00:06:44.519 --> 00:06:45.079
Why are you so hot?

00:06:45.279 --> 00:06:45.680
It's okay.

00:06:45.680 --> 00:06:46.279
Hang in there.

00:06:46.279 --> 00:06:47.399
I'll call Xu Xuejiao to save you.

00:06:47.399 --> 00:06:48.399
Let me help you up first.

00:06:49.680 --> 00:06:50.279
Let's go.

00:06:53.199 --> 00:06:54.000
Don't go.

00:06:54.759 --> 00:06:55.480
Hold me tight.

00:06:55.480 --> 00:06:56.279
I'm not...

00:06:56.480 --> 00:06:57.720
Hey, why should I hold you tight?

00:06:57.720 --> 00:06:57.959
I...

00:06:59.519 --> 00:07:00.199
Don't move, don't move.

00:07:00.199 --> 00:07:01.160
Testing me again.

00:07:01.199 --> 00:07:02.360
I'm a man too.

00:07:02.519 --> 00:07:04.600
If we keep hugging, you'll be in danger again.

00:07:04.920 --> 00:07:05.680
Danger?

00:07:05.680 --> 00:07:06.680
What danger?

00:07:07.519 --> 00:07:08.319
What?

00:07:08.920 --> 00:07:10.480
She can hear my inner thoughts too?

00:07:12.680 --> 00:07:13.519
Chengwen.

00:07:31.959 --> 00:07:32.680
Help!

00:07:33.560 --> 00:07:34.120
Help!

00:07:37.160 --> 00:07:37.959
Mengyun!

00:07:38.199 --> 00:07:39.000
Lu Chengwen!

00:07:39.160 --> 00:07:40.120
What's going on?

00:07:40.399 --> 00:07:40.959
Xu Xuejiao!

00:07:40.959 --> 00:07:41.920
You're just in time.

00:07:41.920 --> 00:07:42.879
Hurry and save her!

00:07:42.879 --> 00:07:44.160
She was drugged by Jiao Shiheng.

00:07:44.279 --> 00:07:45.079
Oh.

00:07:45.959 --> 00:07:46.519
Chengwen...

00:07:46.519 --> 00:07:47.480
Oh my god.

00:07:49.680 --> 00:07:50.480
Lu Chengwen!

00:07:50.800 --> 00:07:52.560
What did you do to Ms. Mengyun?

00:07:55.759 --> 00:07:56.519
It wasn't me!

00:07:56.519 --> 00:07:57.319
It wasn't me!

00:07:58.120 --> 00:07:59.000
Darn it, darn it.

00:07:59.120 --> 00:08:00.920
So if Jiao Shiheng touches Chen Mengyun,

00:08:01.079 --> 00:08:02.279
Gu Zhantian will show up!

00:08:02.879 --> 00:08:04.480
I shouldn't have interfered.

00:08:04.680 --> 00:08:06.319
Can someone explain this for me?

00:08:07.800 --> 00:08:09.120
How about you turn yourself in?

00:08:09.279 --> 00:08:10.519
I'll hold them off.

00:08:11.879 --> 00:08:12.480
Right!

00:08:12.480 --> 00:08:13.279
I'll turn myself in.

00:08:13.680 --> 00:08:15.120
I'll take Jiao Shiheng and turn myself in.

00:08:28.680 --> 00:08:30.120
It's hard being a good guy.

00:08:30.680 --> 00:08:32.279
I got myself involved again.

00:08:34.559 --> 00:08:35.360
Lu Chengwen.

00:08:35.600 --> 00:08:37.120
We've finished our investigation.

00:08:37.279 --> 00:08:38.480
You can leave now.

00:08:41.679 --> 00:08:42.519
You can go.

00:08:42.519 --> 00:08:43.279
Let's go.

00:08:53.080 --> 00:08:53.879
Mr. Lu,

00:08:54.080 --> 00:08:55.120
are you okay?

00:08:55.799 --> 00:08:56.759
I'm fine, I'm fine.

00:08:56.919 --> 00:08:57.960
Just a trip back home.

00:08:58.080 --> 00:08:58.919
What could happen?

00:09:00.399 --> 00:09:00.919
No wonder

00:09:00.919 --> 00:09:02.279
you turned yourself in so smoothly.

00:09:03.559 --> 00:09:04.360
Chengwen,

00:09:05.080 --> 00:09:07.000
I knew you'd come to save me.

00:09:10.679 --> 00:09:11.519
I'm sorry.

00:09:11.960 --> 00:09:13.679
I shouldn't have thrown a tantrum at you.

00:09:14.679 --> 00:09:15.320
It's okay,

00:09:15.320 --> 00:09:15.919
Mengyun.

00:09:15.919 --> 00:09:16.919
It's all in the past.

00:09:17.480 --> 00:09:18.279
Darn it.

00:09:18.600 --> 00:09:20.120
I just took out

00:09:20.120 --> 00:09:21.399
Gu Zhantian's entire team.

00:09:22.879 --> 00:09:24.000
Since you're fine,

00:09:24.120 --> 00:09:25.320
I'll head back first.

00:09:25.799 --> 00:09:26.600
Qingqiu,

00:09:27.679 --> 00:09:28.799
thanks for earlier.

00:09:28.799 --> 00:09:29.480
If it weren't for you,

00:09:29.480 --> 00:09:31.200
I wouldn't have arrived in time.

00:09:32.159 --> 00:09:33.519
I owe you one.

00:09:33.919 --> 00:09:35.679
And you said there was nothing between you and Chen Mengyun.

00:09:36.759 --> 00:09:37.559
Fine.

00:09:38.120 --> 00:09:40.279
Then I'll have you return the favor right now.

00:09:40.559 --> 00:09:42.519
I want you to get engaged to me next month.

00:09:42.919 --> 00:09:43.519
No way!

00:09:43.519 --> 00:09:44.279
No way!

00:09:44.559 --> 00:09:45.720
Good heavens!

00:09:46.120 --> 00:09:47.720
Do villains have love triangles too?

00:09:47.960 --> 00:09:49.759
Brother Chengwen chased you for three years,

00:09:49.919 --> 00:09:52.320
and you played the innocent girl for three whole years.

00:09:52.480 --> 00:09:53.960
Now you're throwing yourself at him.

00:09:54.120 --> 00:09:55.279
How hilarious.

00:09:56.320 --> 00:09:57.120
Brother Chengwen,

00:09:57.200 --> 00:09:58.759
since you don't want to get engaged to her,

00:09:58.759 --> 00:10:00.159
why not get engaged to me?

00:10:01.159 --> 00:10:02.879
Why are you joining in?

00:10:04.120 --> 00:10:04.919
Chengwen,

00:10:05.120 --> 00:10:06.919
I knew you cared about me.

00:10:07.720 --> 00:10:08.360
No,

00:10:08.360 --> 00:10:08.919
Mengyun,

00:10:08.919 --> 00:10:09.879
don't be like this.

00:10:11.320 --> 00:10:12.080
Mr. Lu,

00:10:12.080 --> 00:10:13.080
didn't you promise

00:10:13.080 --> 00:10:14.519
to take me home

00:10:14.519 --> 00:10:15.720
to be your wife?

00:10:16.720 --> 00:10:17.159
Shihan,

00:10:17.159 --> 00:10:18.080
why are you also...

00:10:18.279 --> 00:10:19.080
Xu Xuejiao,

00:10:19.320 --> 00:10:20.159
you couldn't even be bothered

00:10:20.159 --> 00:10:21.679
to say a word to Lu Chengwen before.

00:10:21.879 --> 00:10:23.080
Why are you fighting with me now?

00:10:23.360 --> 00:10:24.159
If I want to fight for him,

00:10:24.200 --> 00:10:24.720
I will fight for him.

00:10:24.720 --> 00:10:25.519
I'll fight for him all I want.

00:10:25.720 --> 00:10:27.200
Others can only watch.

00:10:30.080 --> 00:10:30.879
Sister Mengyun,

00:10:30.919 --> 00:10:32.080
I'm not talking about you.

00:10:32.200 --> 00:10:33.480
You don't have to give yourself to Brother Chengwen

00:10:33.480 --> 00:10:34.879
just because he saved you.

00:10:35.159 --> 00:10:35.840
You know,

00:10:35.840 --> 00:10:38.320
gratitude and affection are two different things.

00:10:38.759 --> 00:10:40.679
Who says I have no feelings for Brother Chengwen?

00:10:40.799 --> 00:10:42.159
I admire his talent,

00:10:42.480 --> 00:10:43.759
and I like his kindness even more.

00:10:44.279 --> 00:10:45.279
Marrying him

00:10:45.480 --> 00:10:47.000
and raising a family together

00:10:47.080 --> 00:10:48.480
is exactly what I want.

00:10:50.559 --> 00:10:51.120
Chengwen,

00:10:51.480 --> 00:10:52.919
isn't that what you want too?

00:10:53.879 --> 00:10:54.679
I...

00:10:55.159 --> 00:10:55.720
No, you...

00:10:55.720 --> 00:10:57.320
What are you all doing?

00:10:57.559 --> 00:10:58.720
Look at where we are!

00:10:58.720 --> 00:11:00.759
And you're all getting jealous over me here?

00:11:01.159 --> 00:11:02.080
Aren't you ashamed?

00:11:02.120 --> 00:11:02.919
Yeah,

00:11:02.919 --> 00:11:04.200
what's wrong with me?

00:11:04.600 --> 00:11:06.679
But my heart really hurts.

00:11:07.519 --> 00:11:08.159
The Lu Chengwen

00:11:08.159 --> 00:11:09.600
who used to obey my every command

00:11:09.600 --> 00:11:10.879
is really gone.

00:11:11.320 --> 00:11:12.480
Why did I become unimportant to him

00:11:12.480 --> 00:11:14.279
overnight?

00:11:14.480 --> 00:11:15.320
Qingqiu,

00:11:15.320 --> 00:11:16.919
why don't you all go home first?

00:11:17.120 --> 00:11:18.120
I'll visit your place another day,

00:11:18.120 --> 00:11:19.039
and we can properly

00:11:19.039 --> 00:11:19.919
discuss this.

00:11:20.320 --> 00:11:21.679
I believe there's

00:11:21.679 --> 00:11:23.200
more than one way to solve this.

00:11:23.200 --> 00:11:24.000
Right?

00:11:24.080 --> 00:11:24.799
Okay.

00:11:24.799 --> 00:11:25.960
I'll wait for your call.

00:11:32.000 --> 00:11:32.720
Lu Chengwen,

00:11:32.720 --> 00:11:34.399
you're not going to be her simp, are you?

00:11:35.200 --> 00:11:36.000
Chengwen,

00:11:36.320 --> 00:11:37.799
you're not going to get engaged to her,

00:11:37.799 --> 00:11:38.399
right?

00:11:40.360 --> 00:11:41.399
Xuejiao, Mengyun,

00:11:41.399 --> 00:11:43.000
why don't you two head back first?

00:11:43.159 --> 00:11:44.320
We'll talk another day.

00:11:44.679 --> 00:11:45.080
Shihan,

00:11:45.080 --> 00:11:45.879
let's go.